summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 to 6 inclusive, Acre 1, Block 46, Maple Leaf Addition to Green Lake Circle, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-237 and 17-183, respectively, and authorizing set-back agreements in connection with such rezoning.
